texts.label: paragraph
texts.orig: If you need to enable SSL in ProFTPD, try this out:
texts.text: If you need to enable SSL in ProFTPD, try this out:

texts.label: code
texts.orig:
<IfModule mod_tls.c>
    TLSEngine on
    TLSRequired off
    TLSRSACertificateFile /etc/httpd/conf/ssl.crt/server.crt
    TLSRSACertificateKeyFile /etc/httpd/conf/ssl.key/server.key
    TLSVerifyClient off
</IfModule>
texts.text:
<IfModule mod_tls.c>
    TLSEngine on
    TLSRequired off
    TLSRSACertificateFile /etc/httpd/conf/ssl.crt/server.crt
    TLSRSACertificateKeyFile /etc/httpd/conf/ssl.key/server.key
    TLSVerifyClient off
</IfModule>
